### Career Intelligence Platform — HTTP Tests
### Import into Postman OR run with IntelliJ HTTP Client

@base = http://localhost:8080
@token = {{authToken}}

### ═══════════════════════════════════════
### 🔐 AUTH — Signup
### ═══════════════════════════════════════
POST {{base}}/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Rahul Sharma",
  "email": "rahul@cip.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "role": "STUDENT"
}

###
### 🔐 AUTH — Login
POST {{base}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "rahul@cip.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

###
### 🔐 AUTH — Get Current User
GET {{base}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
### ═══════════════════════════════════════
### 👤 STUDENT — Get Profile
### ═══════════════════════════════════════
GET {{base}}/student/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
### 👤 STUDENT — Update Profile
PUT {{base}}/student/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "+91-9876543210",
  "institution": "IIT Indore",
  "department": "Computer Science",
  "graduationYear": 2025,
  "skills": [
    {"name": "Java", "proficiency": "ADVANCED", "yearsExperience": 2},
    {"name": "Spring Boot", "proficiency": "INTERMEDIATE", "yearsExperience": 1},
    {"name": "SQL", "proficiency": "INTERMEDIATE", "yearsExperience": 2}
  ],
  "academicData": {
    "cgpa": 8.1,
    "currentSemester": 7,
    "totalSemesters": 8,
    "degree": "B.Tech",
    "specialization": "Software Engineering",
    "subjects": ["DSA", "DBMS", "OS", "CN"],
    "achievements": ["SIH 2023 Winner"]
  }
}

###
### ═══════════════════════════════════════
### 🧠 SCORE — Get My Score
### ═══════════════════════════════════════
GET {{base}}/score
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
### ═══════════════════════════════════════
### 📊 ANALYTICS — Get My Analytics
### ═══════════════════════════════════════
GET {{base}}/analytics
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
### ═══════════════════════════════════════
### 🤖 INTERVIEW — Start
### ═══════════════════════════════════════
POST {{base}}/interview/start
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "TECHNICAL",
  "jobRole": "Backend Engineer",
  "numberOfQuestions": 5
}

###
### 🤖 INTERVIEW — Submit Answer
POST {{base}}/interview/answer
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "interviewId": 1,
  "questionIndex": 0,
  "answer": "A thread is a lightweight unit of execution within a process. Threads share the same memory space but have their own stack, register set, and program counter. Processes are heavyweight with separate memory spaces.",
  "timeTakenSeconds": 90
}

###
### 🤖 INTERVIEW — End Session
POST {{base}}/interview/end?interviewId=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
### 🤖 INTERVIEW — Get Result
GET {{base}}/interview/result/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
### 🤖 INTERVIEW — History
GET {{base}}/interview/history
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
### ═══════════════════════════════════════
### 🎯 JOBS — All Jobs
### ═══════════════════════════════════════
GET {{base}}/jobs?page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
### 🎯 JOBS — Recommended (pass readiness + skills)
GET {{base}}/jobs/recommended?readiness=68&skills=Java&skills=Spring Boot&skills=SQL
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
### ═══════════════════════════════════════
### 🗺 ROADMAP
### ═══════════════════════════════════════
GET {{base}}/roadmap?role=backend-engineer&level=Almost+Ready&skills=Java&skills=SQL
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
### 🗺 SKILL RECOMMENDATIONS
GET {{base}}/recommendations/skills?readiness=68&skills=Java&skills=SQL&targetRole=backend-engineer
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
### ═══════════════════════════════════════
### 📄 RESUME — Upload (use multipart in Postman)
### ═══════════════════════════════════════
# POST {{base}}/resume/upload
# Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
# Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----FormBoundary
# (attach file=<your-resume.pdf>)

###
### 📄 RESUME — Get All Resumes
GET {{base}}/resume
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

